2
00:00:14,579 --> 00:00:21,273
<i>Spring 2000</i>

3
00:00:21,856 --> 00:00:23,626
<i>Letter number 53!</i>

4
00:00:23,746 --> 00:00:25,696
<i>You’re finally discharged from the army.</i>

5
00:00:25,796 --> 00:00:26,761
<i>Congratulations friend!</i>

6
00:00:26,817 --> 00:00:28,674
Hey friend!

7
00:00:29,319 --> 00:00:31,007
- Sang Hoon.
- Long time no see.

8
00:00:31,298 --> 00:00:33,370
It’s been a while.

9
00:00:33,612 --> 00:00:35,806
About 2 years I think.

10
00:00:36,144 --> 00:00:37,280
Where’s Nan Hee?

11
00:00:37,402 --> 00:00:39,045
Behind you.

12
00:00:41,653 --> 00:00:43,356
I was here for awhile,

13
00:00:43,522 --> 00:00:44,980
you finally notice me.

14
00:00:45,072 --> 00:00:48,840
Hey, what's wrong with you?

15
00:00:50,489 --> 00:00:51,361
What’s with her?

16
00:00:51,437 --> 00:00:55,258
She got dumped by her boyfriend
and showed up like this.

17
00:00:55,350 --> 00:00:57,529
I don’t know if we should
acknowledge her as a friend or not.

18
00:00:57,652 --> 00:01:00,116
We’re still thinking.

19
00:01:06,456 --> 00:01:08,343
Hyung Tae.

20
00:01:12,664 --> 00:01:13,692
You smoke now?

21
00:01:13,799 --> 00:01:16,601
I think I'm going crazy.

22
00:01:17,006 --> 00:01:20,000
You’re a mess right now.

23
00:01:20,275 --> 00:01:25,445
I’m gone for 3 years in the
damn army while you're like this.

24
00:01:29,679 --> 00:01:31,176
Nan Hee.

25
00:01:31,567 --> 00:01:36,777
When you visited me last time, I want to
thank you for not keeping your promise.

26
00:01:36,937 --> 00:01:38,734
Hyung Tae.

27
00:01:39,608 --> 00:01:41,435
Seung Won.

28
00:01:45,252 --> 00:01:49,140
<i>The first impression was like Scarlet O’Hara.</i>

29
00:01:52,185 --> 00:01:53,713
You’re back.

30
00:01:55,328 --> 00:01:56,310
Who’s that?

31
00:01:56,417 --> 00:01:57,645
Isn’t she Yoon Sung Ah?

32
00:01:57,722 --> 00:01:58,965
You know her?

33
00:01:59,087 --> 00:02:01,205
She’s visiting Korea.

34
00:02:01,427 --> 00:02:04,345
She’s our special guest.

35
00:02:04,716 --> 00:02:09,711
I thought she would refuse but
she said okay without a problem.

36
00:02:12,684 --> 00:02:14,418
<i>2000 spring.</i>

37
00:02:14,571 --> 00:02:17,088
<i>She came into our lives like the wind.</i>

38
00:02:17,164 --> 00:02:19,843
Seung Won, is it hard to learn guitar?

39
00:02:24,847 --> 00:02:28,852
Hey! Hey, you know, right?
Answer for me.

40
00:02:28,914 --> 00:02:31,891
Hey! Hey! How can I take roll for you. Hey!

41
00:02:44,444 --> 00:02:45,288
Byun Hyung Tae.

42
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:46,393
He’s not here.

43
00:02:52,526 --> 00:02:53,846
Nan Hee.

44
00:02:53,923 --> 00:02:54,636
What about roll?

45
00:02:54,828 --> 00:02:55,919
I did it.

46
00:02:56,224 --> 00:02:57,145
What about mine?

47
00:02:57,222 --> 00:02:58,551
Of course.

48
00:03:03,179 --> 00:03:05,283
Can you guys separate a little?

49
00:03:05,489 --> 00:03:07,592
I can see you guys sweating.

50
00:03:10,842 --> 00:03:12,929
Stop it, stop it, stop it.

51
00:03:24,897 --> 00:03:28,795
<i>We couldn’t imagine ourselves without her anymore.</i>

52
00:03:35,995 --> 00:03:37,860
Who’s this?

53
00:03:38,082 --> 00:03:41,397
I’m a little nervous because
we haven’t talked for so long.

54
00:03:41,532 --> 00:03:44,854
You were the same way when
you were dating. Don’t complain.

55
00:03:45,046 --> 00:03:46,304
That’s scary.

56
00:03:46,519 --> 00:03:48,959
You’re trying to get away with it by using my first
dating experience as an excuse, aren't you?

57
00:03:49,097 --> 00:03:52,282
Sung Ah's leaving soon.
What are you going to do?

58
00:03:52,534 --> 00:03:53,777
She’s not going.

59
00:03:53,931 --> 00:03:55,267
What?

60
00:03:55,473 --> 00:03:57,491
She said she'll stay.

61
00:03:57,652 --> 00:03:58,680
What?

62
00:03:58,757 --> 00:04:00,643
Didn’t she have to make a record?

63
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:03,367
Aren’t her parents in Spain?

64
00:04:03,604 --> 00:04:05,716
She wants to be with me.

65
00:04:06,443 --> 00:04:09,928
How come everything happens
on a whim for her?

66
00:04:11,526 --> 00:04:13,076
That’s why I’m worried.

67
00:04:13,199 --> 00:04:14,718
I bet you are.

68
00:04:14,979 --> 00:04:18,578
You’re only 23 and it's not
like you can take care of her.

69
00:04:18,769 --> 00:04:23,472
Wait a minute. Are you even capable to do so?

70
00:04:23,554 --> 00:04:25,526
Think carefully.

71
00:04:25,809 --> 00:04:36,051
Nan Hee, what if one day Sung Ah leaves me
just like she decided to leave her career?

72
00:04:36,208 --> 00:04:38,863
You’re both crazy.

73
00:04:39,016 --> 00:04:42,155
Yeah , we're both crazy.

74
00:05:16,919 --> 00:05:18,561
It should be okay.

75
00:05:19,305 --> 00:05:21,891
It’s raining a lot though.

76
00:05:22,021 --> 00:05:23,571
It’s too much for a hike.

77
00:05:23,632 --> 00:05:25,723
It’s not much. I heard it'll stop later.

78
00:05:25,885 --> 00:05:28,202
Still that course is pretty rough.

79
00:05:28,355 --> 00:05:29,506
Let’s forget it.

80
00:05:29,629 --> 00:05:33,304
Yeah, let’s go after the rain.
We can go tomorrow too.

81
00:05:33,498 --> 00:05:35,040
It will be okay.

82
00:05:35,171 --> 00:05:37,779
Let’s just go. It’s Sung Ah’s birthday.

83
00:05:37,933 --> 00:05:40,296
We came to hike and Hyung Tae won’t give in.

84
00:05:40,373 --> 00:05:41,101
You’re right.

85
00:05:41,278 --> 00:05:42,423
Let's go.

86
00:05:57,616 --> 00:05:58,713
Seung Won.

87
00:05:58,943 --> 00:06:00,101
It’s okay, just go.

88
00:06:00,293 --> 00:06:02,259
- You got it?
- Yeah.

89
00:06:10,396 --> 00:06:12,001
Seung Won!

90
00:06:12,790 --> 00:06:14,871
What happened?

91
00:06:15,077 --> 00:06:16,059
Seung Won!

92
00:06:16,105 --> 00:06:17,164
Seung Won!

93
00:06:17,256 --> 00:06:18,637
What do we do?!

94
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:21,161
Seung Won.

95
00:06:25,281 --> 00:06:32,944
<i>Through that accident we lost a friend and
while we were all mourning, she left us.</i>

96
00:06:33,043 --> 00:06:36,970
<i>She didn’t leave anything for Hyung Tae,</i>

97
00:06:37,077 --> 00:06:41,712
<i>and without any reason, she just left us.</i>

98
00:06:41,834 --> 00:06:45,935
<i>And now, the sadness is barely healing.</i>

99
00:06:50,317 --> 00:06:51,897
<i>Why aren’t you coming?</i>

100
00:06:51,959 --> 00:06:54,522
<i>What time are the tickets?</i>

101
00:06:58,201 --> 00:07:00,382
[Love Letter]

102
00:07:12,365 --> 00:07:14,284
[Sung Ah]

103
00:07:24,236 --> 00:07:25,494
Try some kiwi, it's good.

104
00:07:25,633 --> 00:07:28,480
Eat a lot okay?

105
00:08:09,318 --> 00:08:10,846
<i>It's me.</i>

106
00:08:13,995 --> 00:08:16,458
<i>Say something.</i>

107
00:08:21,453 --> 00:08:23,126
<i>Hyung Tae.</i>

108
00:08:25,207 --> 00:08:26,405
Yeah.

109
00:08:28,214 --> 00:08:30,464
What should I say?

110
00:08:32,312 --> 00:08:34,899
<i>Did I come too late?</i>

111
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:44,351
<i>Since this phone was off, that means
I’m past the expiration date, right?</i>

112
00:08:46,746 --> 00:08:47,867
Yes.

113
00:08:48,143 --> 00:08:49,924
You're right.

114
00:08:50,843 --> 00:08:52,701
I’m sorry.

115
00:08:54,311 --> 00:08:56,499
<i>You shouldn’t be.</i>

116
00:08:58,192 --> 00:08:59,543
Yeah.

117
00:09:00,801 --> 00:09:02,774
Why should I be?

118
00:09:07,553 --> 00:09:09,524
Byun Hyung Tae!

119
00:09:09,761 --> 00:09:12,717
Byun Hyung Tae! You really look like a
member who works for the society.

120
00:10:04,526 --> 00:10:06,660
Why isn’t he coming?

121
00:10:06,966 --> 00:10:08,386
He's coming now.

122
00:10:08,570 --> 00:10:10,466
Right here.

123
00:10:37,395 --> 00:10:39,758
Can I get some attention too?

124
00:10:39,927 --> 00:10:40,771
What's going on?

125
00:10:40,925 --> 00:10:43,649
Are you two together again?

126
00:10:43,812 --> 00:10:47,088
No. Jun Mo had to meet her
for work, so he brought her.

127
00:10:57,494 --> 00:10:58,995
I missed you guys.

128
00:10:59,133 --> 00:11:05,219
Hey! You're the one that
left us and now you miss us?

129
00:11:05,839 --> 00:11:07,321
You're right.

130
00:11:08,384 --> 00:11:09,881
They seem quite intense with each other.

131
00:11:10,195 --> 00:11:13,580
Well... I guess they are a bit.

132
00:11:14,108 --> 00:11:16,640
Do you have any idea what
Hyung Tae went through?

133
00:11:17,941 --> 00:11:20,427
Hey, are you guys watching out for me?

134
00:11:20,519 --> 00:11:24,325
You guys are really great.
But I’m okay, so take let's stop the tension.

135
00:11:24,463 --> 00:11:30,521
What about us?
We were all best friends, then suddenly...

136
00:11:30,629 --> 00:11:33,147
Stop it already.
None of you are kids anymore.

137
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:35,640
I’m glad you're here.

138
00:11:42,753 --> 00:11:45,824
- Nan Hee should ride with me.
- Huh?

139
00:11:46,681 --> 00:11:49,620
Let’s go, they should get some privacy.

140
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:55,532
Does he actually still like her after all that?

141
00:11:55,976 --> 00:11:58,133
Does he?

142
00:11:59,153 --> 00:12:00,853
Nan Hee, let's go.

143
00:12:01,174 --> 00:12:03,522
We decided to ride with Jun Mo.

144
00:12:03,660 --> 00:12:05,425
Why? We go the same way.

145
00:12:05,502 --> 00:12:08,741
It's okay. You two should talk.

146
00:12:09,062 --> 00:12:10,566
There's nothing to talk about.

147
00:12:10,675 --> 00:12:13,891
Let’s meet again.
We didn’t get to talk much.

148
00:12:14,159 --> 00:12:17,013
Nan Hee, Let’s have a girls' night out.

149
00:12:17,228 --> 00:12:18,633
Okay.

150
00:12:38,523 --> 00:12:40,303
What are you thinking about?

151
00:12:40,518 --> 00:12:41,678
Huh?

152
00:12:43,648 --> 00:12:46,410
That I’m going home.

153
00:12:46,579 --> 00:12:49,519
That's not much to think about.

154
00:12:51,382 --> 00:12:53,499
It's pretty important to me.

155
00:12:53,596 --> 00:12:54,871
Well then...

156
00:13:02,758 --> 00:13:07,297
It doesn’t mean anything whether
Sung Ah is back or not. So don’t think...

157
00:13:07,343 --> 00:13:09,570
You don’t have to say it.

158
00:13:12,116 --> 00:13:14,680
I know what you're going to say.

159
00:13:16,543 --> 00:13:19,099
You want to be alone, right?

160
00:13:22,666 --> 00:13:24,124
No.

161
00:13:26,918 --> 00:13:32,168
Don’t you think we don’t get
enough personal time these days?

162
00:13:41,695 --> 00:13:43,055
Here.

163
00:13:45,056 --> 00:13:47,206
You're going to sleep?

164
00:13:47,412 --> 00:13:48,340
Yes.

165
00:13:50,757 --> 00:13:52,285
Alright.

166
00:15:03,414 --> 00:15:05,442
Ah! The movie.

167
00:15:09,599 --> 00:15:11,111
Nan Hee.

168
00:15:12,397 --> 00:15:14,132
Nan Hee.

169
00:15:15,021 --> 00:15:16,496
Nan Hee.

170
00:16:24,576 --> 00:16:26,496
I’m sorry.

171
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:39,116
This time, I kept my promise.

172
00:16:39,381 --> 00:16:40,686
Yeah.

173
00:16:43,187 --> 00:16:44,638
Look at that.

174
00:16:44,859 --> 00:16:51,241
That's her letting go of the man
she kept in her heart.

175
00:16:51,738 --> 00:16:55,200
It's really moving.

176
00:16:57,585 --> 00:17:01,697
<i>Are you doing well?</i>

177
00:17:04,312 --> 00:17:09,523
<i>I’m doing fine.</i>

178
00:17:40,822 --> 00:17:43,086
You should yell at me.

179
00:17:44,035 --> 00:17:46,046
I said I’m sorry.

180
00:17:46,199 --> 00:17:48,526
You want to hit me?

181
00:17:49,667 --> 00:17:54,003
I’m really a bad person.
It was supposed to be our first date.

182
00:17:54,797 --> 00:17:59,209
I'll forgive you since you're sorry.

183
00:17:59,401 --> 00:18:00,614
Really?

184
00:18:01,380 --> 00:18:06,788
It's understandable since it was
a shocking incident today.

185
00:18:07,355 --> 00:18:10,854
Is there another girl as great as you?

186
00:18:11,099 --> 00:18:13,677
You're my best friend and my girlfriend.

187
00:18:13,892 --> 00:18:16,632
I’m really a lucky guy.

188
00:18:21,198 --> 00:18:23,493
But let’s end it.

189
00:18:23,991 --> 00:18:26,715
It wasn’t as if we were officially a couple,

190
00:18:26,958 --> 00:18:32,191
but still let's forget about
this confusing relationship.

191
00:18:32,252 --> 00:18:33,111
Hey!

192
00:18:33,265 --> 00:18:37,623
Sung Ah came back to get with you.

193
00:18:37,866 --> 00:18:39,569
Are you really going to ignore her?

194
00:18:39,723 --> 00:18:41,058
Why does it matter?

195
00:18:41,150 --> 00:18:43,407
I don’t care.

196
00:18:43,697 --> 00:18:45,893
Can’t you trust me?

197
00:18:46,275 --> 00:18:48,070
There's that line all men use.

198
00:18:48,169 --> 00:18:49,029
Nan Hee.

199
00:18:49,167 --> 00:18:50,548
I don’t like this.

200
00:18:50,778 --> 00:18:56,480
It's uncomfortable to hear things come out of
your mouth that hasn’t for last 30 years.

201
00:18:56,655 --> 00:18:59,787
I think Byun Hyung Tae,
the boyfriend, is whatever.

202
00:18:59,963 --> 00:19:02,695
I can’t even say what I want.

203
00:19:02,832 --> 00:19:04,535
Same for you too.

204
00:19:04,704 --> 00:19:07,406
It was so much easier before.

205
00:19:07,709 --> 00:19:12,650
When one of us was feeling trashy,
the other would be the trash can.

206
00:19:12,819 --> 00:19:15,904
Sometimes we would cheer for
each other no matter what.

207
00:19:16,325 --> 00:19:22,143
We were able to stop and go for each other
and that's the kind of friendship we had.

208
00:19:25,379 --> 00:19:28,988
Whenever I wanted to cry,
you were the first on my mind.

209
00:19:29,141 --> 00:19:30,661
You probably were the same.

210
00:19:30,829 --> 00:19:33,055
Look at us now.

211
00:19:33,269 --> 00:19:36,078
It wasn’t long ago when you spent
my money to go to Spain.

212
00:19:36,156 --> 00:19:38,320
I doubt you forgot about her already.

213
00:19:38,412 --> 00:19:41,107
She meant a lot to you.

214
00:19:41,635 --> 00:19:45,556
I bet it was killing you inside to act
like nothing happened today.

215
00:19:45,717 --> 00:19:48,426
You're hurting more than anyone right now.

216
00:19:48,640 --> 00:19:50,543
And you're trying so hard to hide that from me.

217
00:19:50,620 --> 00:19:53,146
Don’t you think I know how you feel?

218
00:19:56,175 --> 00:19:59,475
Because I know how you feel,

219
00:20:00,993 --> 00:20:04,316
I can’t really do anything.

220
00:20:05,458 --> 00:20:07,493
Damn it, seriously.

221
00:20:17,796 --> 00:20:20,138
Hey, are you crying?

222
00:20:25,418 --> 00:20:29,132
Be quiet. Can’t you pretend you don’t know?

223
00:20:30,160 --> 00:20:34,258
It was too obvious to pretend.

224
00:20:35,062 --> 00:20:37,558
I’m so angry.

225
00:20:41,922 --> 00:20:43,971
Do you want a hug?

226
00:20:45,021 --> 00:20:46,542
Oh my.

227
00:20:56,110 --> 00:21:02,997
She asked if canceling the phone
meant that I’m over her.

228
00:21:03,509 --> 00:21:06,871
She definitely came back for you.

229
00:21:08,321 --> 00:21:10,501
How did you know?

230
00:21:11,543 --> 00:21:15,926
I never thought she would be
back but she came back.

231
00:21:18,999 --> 00:21:23,343
I feel better now that I told you.

232
00:21:24,109 --> 00:21:27,034
You like me better as a friend, right?

233
00:21:28,926 --> 00:21:34,445
Half and half. I wish there were two of you.

234
00:21:39,453 --> 00:21:41,556
I really do like you.

235
00:21:42,499 --> 00:21:47,027
If you didn’t reject me,
I wanted to keep dating you.

236
00:21:49,036 --> 00:21:56,077
I don’t think I ever had
that much courage before.

237
00:21:57,740 --> 00:22:01,960
I knew if I told you how I feel,
there was a lot we could lose.

238
00:22:02,288 --> 00:22:05,521
I thought about it and thought about it.

239
00:22:07,583 --> 00:22:12,442
But after, it was so much fun.

240
00:22:14,097 --> 00:22:20,375
I can finally date someone with ease and joy.

241
00:22:21,570 --> 00:22:25,815
Just the fact I can date like
this at age 30 was great.

242
00:22:29,204 --> 00:22:33,733
The hand that I held thousands of times
before became something more.

243
00:22:35,272 --> 00:22:39,011
The small jokes I spit out
suddenly had meaning.

244
00:22:41,441 --> 00:22:43,974
I enjoyed it a lot.

245
00:22:44,707 --> 00:22:47,786
It amazed me that it was happening.

246
00:22:49,894 --> 00:22:52,965
I can’t do this with any other woman,

247
00:22:54,498 --> 00:22:59,487
these are things that I can only do with you.

248
00:23:01,288 --> 00:23:06,169
As sweet as that sounds, I like it hot.

249
00:23:06,444 --> 00:23:08,828
You're talking about that brat.

250
00:23:09,103 --> 00:23:14,153
I hope you and Sung Ah
feel something hot as well.

251
00:23:14,765 --> 00:23:16,776
Don’t push me.

252
00:23:16,883 --> 00:23:19,679
I’m a little confused.

253
00:23:21,610 --> 00:23:24,189
The ball is on your side now.

254
00:23:24,418 --> 00:23:26,383
Just hit it.

255
00:23:26,521 --> 00:23:29,731
It will either complete your love,

256
00:23:29,914 --> 00:23:34,435
or if it doesn’t work out,
just walk out and leave.

257
00:23:35,040 --> 00:23:40,029
Make sure your heart can have a resolve.

258
00:23:41,229 --> 00:23:45,357
At your state now, no matter whom you meet.

259
00:23:45,587 --> 00:23:50,069
Sung Ah will always be in your mind.

260
00:23:50,325 --> 00:23:52,705
You think you're so great, don’t you.

261
00:23:53,118 --> 00:23:55,312
I’m going to work on my book.

262
00:23:55,542 --> 00:23:58,136
The deadline's coming up,

263
00:23:58,320 --> 00:24:02,688
and I don’t have time to get
in your triangle of love.

264
00:24:02,978 --> 00:24:05,480
I’m doing this for my mom,

265
00:24:05,909 --> 00:24:06,822
I have to make it.

266
00:24:06,999 --> 00:24:10,146
Okay, stop. I got it.

267
00:24:14,355 --> 00:24:16,151
Us...

268
00:24:19,741 --> 00:24:22,964
How long do you think we can be friends?

269
00:24:31,181 --> 00:24:36,519
When we were in our 20's,
we drifted due to dating.

270
00:24:36,894 --> 00:24:40,418
But now we have to get married.

271
00:24:41,298 --> 00:24:44,223
We would still see each other.

272
00:24:44,519 --> 00:24:47,390
But it's going to be different.

273
00:24:48,647 --> 00:24:52,047
I don’t know where we would be,

274
00:24:53,048 --> 00:24:58,006
but one day we would say something like,

275
00:24:59,045 --> 00:25:07,895
Was there ever a time when
we were actually friends?

276
00:25:14,775 --> 00:25:17,239
Stop thinking that.

277
00:25:17,644 --> 00:25:20,177
Just go on as much as we can.

278
00:25:20,498 --> 00:25:21,927
Okay?

279
00:25:22,785 --> 00:25:24,337
Okay.

280
00:25:31,418 --> 00:25:32,755
Let’s go.

281
00:25:34,944 --> 00:25:36,356
You go in first.

282
00:25:36,510 --> 00:25:38,928
I’m staying for a bit.

283
00:25:55,126 --> 00:26:03,719
