294
00:28:21,257 --> 00:28:22,093
Friend!

295
00:28:22,232 --> 00:28:24,449
Do you want to go running?

296
00:28:25,078 --> 00:28:26,353
Alright.

297
00:28:26,988 --> 00:28:29,029
Did you write more?

298
00:28:29,167 --> 00:28:30,218
See it later.

299
00:28:30,310 --> 00:28:31,608
Why?

300
00:28:31,707 --> 00:28:34,232
I’m just testing printing.

301
00:28:34,408 --> 00:28:35,413
Let’s go.

302
00:28:35,505 --> 00:28:36,880
Let’s go.

303
00:28:50,919 --> 00:28:55,453
<i>One step closer, one step further</i>

304
00:28:55,675 --> 00:29:00,438
<i>I'm sick of going backward, forward like this</i>

305
00:29:00,642 --> 00:29:04,965
<i>If you like me just say so</i>

306
00:29:05,126 --> 00:29:09,073
<i>Let's not waste our effort</i>

307
00:29:09,250 --> 00:29:14,324
<i>My love, I love you.</i>

308
00:29:26,360 --> 00:29:27,247
What?

309
00:29:27,404 --> 00:29:29,421
Give me the $230.

310
00:29:30,482 --> 00:29:32,492
You're breaking up so soon.

311
00:29:32,858 --> 00:29:34,752
This is not damaged, right?

312
00:29:34,911 --> 00:29:37,428
I'm selling this on the internet.

313
00:29:37,857 --> 00:29:40,263
What kind of relationship is this?
It's not a 3-minute fast food, you know.

314
00:29:40,434 --> 00:29:42,353
Yet it's over so quickly!

315
00:29:42,778 --> 00:29:44,313
And what are all these books?

316
00:29:44,429 --> 00:29:46,130
Joo Young's novel is almost ready.

317
00:29:46,232 --> 00:29:48,674
I have to look for other writers now.

318
00:29:50,549 --> 00:29:52,579
You were dumped?

319
00:29:54,833 --> 00:29:56,824
$230!

320
00:30:02,949 --> 00:30:03,724
Yes?

321
00:30:03,848 --> 00:30:05,932
<i>Nan Hee! I've done it!</i>

322
00:30:06,364 --> 00:30:07,270
What?

323
00:30:07,329 --> 00:30:09,639
He said he'll forgive me and
he'll take it as it didn't happen.

324
00:30:09,827 --> 00:30:11,312
That's really great.

325
00:30:11,548 --> 00:30:13,644
I've been worried sick,
now I can finally relax a little.

326
00:30:13,719 --> 00:30:15,532
This is really good news indeed.

327
00:30:15,795 --> 00:30:17,794
Why were you worried sick?

328
00:30:17,927 --> 00:30:20,313
Oh, nothing much. It's over now.

329
00:30:20,547 --> 00:30:22,549
That's great.

330
00:30:23,243 --> 00:30:26,573
- Anyhow, I'm so grateful to him.
- Yes.

331
00:30:27,078 --> 00:30:29,928
- Or maybe I should buy him a gift?
- Yes, go ahead.

332
00:30:30,172 --> 00:30:31,822
