333
00:30:32,094 --> 00:30:34,258
A man who's in his forties...

334
00:30:34,437 --> 00:30:35,762
What's good for him?

335
00:30:35,938 --> 00:30:37,985
Forties?

336
00:30:38,612 --> 00:30:40,722
Where is it?

337
00:30:49,203 --> 00:30:51,141
How about shoes?

338
00:30:51,444 --> 00:30:52,580
Would that be too expensive?

339
00:30:52,783 --> 00:30:53,957
Who says so?

340
00:30:54,116 --> 00:30:56,642
Even if I had to spend all my salary,
I should still buy it for him.

341
00:30:56,809 --> 00:30:58,268
But I don't know his size.

342
00:30:58,396 --> 00:31:01,253
Just buy the closest size and
