343
00:31:01,570 --> 00:31:02,930
Wait a minute...

344
00:31:03,488 --> 00:31:04,983
Director Im,

345
00:31:05,130 --> 00:31:07,073
What size shoes do you wear?

346
00:31:07,298 --> 00:31:08,998
275. Why?

347
00:31:09,132 --> 00:31:10,564
Nothing.

348
00:31:10,796 --> 00:31:11,743
Hello?

349
00:31:11,961 --> 00:31:13,931
Just buy size 275.

350
00:31:16,994 --> 00:31:19,124
<i>Sung Ah</i>

351
00:31:26,992 --> 00:31:29,075
So you are here.

352
00:31:30,488 --> 00:31:31,844
Oh!

353
00:31:33,463 --> 00:31:36,260
Are you guilty about something?
Why the scare?

354
00:31:37,586 --> 00:31:40,003
So those who are guilty get scared easily?

355
00:31:41,395 --> 00:31:43,087
Shall I let you have this spot?

356
00:31:43,350 --> 00:31:46,221
I'll tell you three shocking things,

357
00:31:46,440 --> 00:31:49,138
Shall I start from the biggest item,
Or shall I start from the smallest?

358
00:31:49,270 --> 00:31:51,509
The middle one.

359
00:31:51,795 --> 00:31:55,777
You and I will be working on
the same project again.

360
00:31:56,075 --> 00:31:58,956
And what will it be this time?

361
00:31:59,658 --> 00:32:01,398
I'm fine with it,

362
00:32:01,580 --> 00:32:03,478
You're... Alright with it too?

363
00:32:03,682 --> 00:32:07,229
If we win it, it'll be a 3-months long project.

364
00:32:07,579 --> 00:32:09,012
A campaign?

365
00:32:09,240 --> 00:32:13,618
The biggest item will have a huge impact on you
so I shall start with the smallest item.

366
00:32:13,827 --> 00:32:15,449
What is it?

367
00:32:15,699 --> 00:32:18,152
I'm being included by my peers.

368
00:32:18,360 --> 00:32:19,822
