be the leader amongst my peers.

373
00:32:38,069 --> 00:32:42,634
And the most shocking piece of news,

374
00:32:44,868 --> 00:32:49,097
This will be our next project.

375
00:33:01,612 --> 00:33:02,457
Hey!

376
00:33:02,641 --> 00:33:05,108
You must have a huge headache, right?

377
00:33:05,393 --> 00:33:07,855
Stop laughing.

378
00:33:08,243 --> 00:33:12,172
It's true. I myself find it hilarious too.

379
00:33:12,323 --> 00:33:14,462
What do you call this?

380
00:33:14,665 --> 00:33:16,850
Hey! Are you Boss Shima Kousaku*?
(*a manhwa character)

381
00:33:16,941 --> 00:33:19,614
The territory of girls you've hugged before is really big.

382
00:33:19,888 --> 00:33:24,088
This time, even a world class guitarist
will join the crowd?

383
00:33:27,709 --> 00:33:31,414
I say, how about try me out too?

384
00:33:31,665 --> 00:33:36,155
I won't hurt you.
You just have to follow me slowly.

385
00:33:38,364 --> 00:33:40,197
Crushing in a broken can, are you?

386
00:33:40,263 --> 00:33:41,487
Really!

387
00:33:41,648 --> 00:33:44,189
Your friend's right.

388
00:33:44,370 --> 00:33:48,220
Your first sight of her and your heart's dropped.

389
00:33:48,459 --> 00:33:49,922
Why are you fighting it?

390
00:33:50,082 --> 00:33:52,122
Is this still...

391
00:33:52,251 --> 00:33:53,481
Love?

392
00:33:53,679 --> 00:33:55,776
Meet her up then check it out.

393
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:59,919
On the other hand,
I'm sick of my current situation.

394
00:34:00,262 --> 00:34:01,647
I like Nan Hee.

395
00:34:01,882 --> 00:34:07,521
But if I asked her to be with me
as I am right now, it'll only hurt her.

396
00:34:08,426 --> 00:34:11,565
If she gets hurt, my heart will ache.

397
00:34:11,793 --> 00:34:14,238
See! You're joined together already.

398
00:34:14,912 --> 00:34:16,721
Didn't you say you wouldn't hurt me?

399
00:34:16,962 --> 00:34:20,698
Fine. Then let's sort this out one by one.

400
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:23,213
When you first heard her voice
on the phone again,

401
00:34:23,348 --> 00:34:26,406
What is the word that came to your mind?

402
00:34:27,431 --> 00:34:29,270
Sung Ah...

403
00:34:30,413 --> 00:34:32,116
She was calling my name.

404
00:34:32,290 --> 00:34:33,590
Game over.

405
00:34:33,689 --> 00:34:35,156
What was that?

406
00:34:35,293 --> 00:34:37,803
You know and yet you ask.

407
00:34:37,989 --> 00:34:41,378
Whether that's love or the remnant
of your missing her,

408
00:34:41,425 --> 00:34:44,939
You're not done with her yet.

409
00:34:45,371 --> 00:34:49,044
Hey! Boss Shima, you'd better solve
this before the project starts.

410
00:34:49,105 --> 00:34:52,082
Who knows? Maybe you'll have
to meet her often in future,

411
00:34:52,129 --> 00:34:55,631
You better not let it affect your work.

412
00:35:06,528 --> 00:35:08,891
<i>Even though living is hard</i>

413
00:35:09,034 --> 00:35:11,306
<i>Even if I fall in love</i>

414
00:35:11,740 --> 00:35:16,558
<i>But someday a good day will come to me too</i>

415
00:35:16,741 --> 00:35:19,058
<i>This is the beginning</i>

416
