00:35:43,622 --> 00:35:47,224
<i>It's suppose to be hard for everyone</i>

420
00:35:47,487 --> 00:35:50,965
<i>After one night's sleep</i>

421
00:35:51,141 --> 00:35:54,485
<i>Everything will be fine again</i>

422
00:35:54,672 --> 00:35:58,863
<i>I don't know how to give up </i>

423
00:35:59,061 --> 00:36:02,195
<i>I'm fine and strong</i>

424
00:36:02,251 --> 00:36:07,581
<i>{\a6}Always cheerful and happy</i>

425
00:36:02,251 --> 00:36:07,581
[Nan Hee, tonight I'll...]

426
00:36:07,582 --> 00:36:09,582
<i>I will patiently endure it</i>

427
00:36:10,007 --> 00:36:10,903
<i>I believe</i>

428
00:36:11,004 --> 00:36:12,474
<i>Even though living is hard </i>

429
00:36:12,692 --> 00:36:14,351
<i>Even if I fall in love</i>

430
00:36:14,550 --> 00:36:18,123
<i>I will never cry or complain </i>

431
00:36:18,375 --> 00:36:19,977
<i>This is the beginning</i>

432
00:36:20,193 --> 00:36:23,276
<i>The star of life is me </i>

433
00:36:23,442 --> 00:36:25,633
<i>I never don't cry</i>

434
00:36:26,427 --> 00:36:28,282
<i>{\a6}Sad tears goodbye</i>

435
00:36:26,427 --> 00:36:28,282
I want to buy this.

436
00:36:28,661 --> 00:36:30,253
<i>{\a6}Hard worries goodbye</i>

437
00:36:28,661 --> 00:36:30,253
