446
00:36:54,159 --> 00:36:55,680
What now?

447
00:36:55,851 --> 00:36:59,072
Recently, she's hooked on bowling,
she's in a semi-retired state.

448
00:36:59,292 --> 00:37:00,419
Guy problems again?

449
00:37:00,665 --> 00:37:02,938
