457
00:37:33,905 --> 00:37:36,680
Ah! Drinks?

458
00:37:38,490 --> 00:37:42,332
Fine. I know a great place.
Shall I show you?

459
00:37:50,059 --> 00:37:52,323
Oh my gosh! Stop fidgeting with it?

460
00:37:52,493 --> 00:37:53,896
It's shedding a layer of skin already.

461
00:37:54,165 --> 00:37:56,028
This book...

462
00:37:56,267 --> 00:38:01,970
