467
00:38:16,327 --> 00:38:17,242
Jung Joo?

468
00:38:17,342 --> 00:38:18,408
Yes.

469
00:38:18,696 --> 00:38:20,064
If I describe it in manhwa terms,

470
00:38:20,202 --> 00:38:27,781
