00:41:01,889 --> 00:41:05,047
<i>{\a6}Even if time passed</i>

494
00:41:01,889 --> 00:41:05,047
Jung Joo!

495
00:41:05,079 --> 00:41:08,849
<i>The memories are still in my heart</i>

496
00:41:10,279 --> 00:41:12,849
How are you?

497
00:41:13,897 --> 00:41:18,005
<i>{\a6}Flowers facing the sky</i>

498
00:41:13,897 --> 00:41:18,005
Are you doing well?

499
00:41:21,006 --> 00:41:24,521
<i>{\a6}I look at you</i>

500
00:41:21,006 --> 00:41:24,521
Jung Joo!

501
00:41:24,600 --> 00:41:27,000
<i>My heart keeps growing</i>

502
00:41:27,864 --> 00:41:32,627
<i>We're always together yet we're blind to it</i>

503
00:41:32,893 --> 00:41:40,339
<i>Like the hands of a clock</i>

504
00:41:40,597 --> 00:41:43,470
<i>Do you see my tears?</i>

505
00:41:43,612 --> 00:41:46,872
<i>Do you hear my voice?</i>

506
00:41:47,103 --> 00:41:50,245
<i>Don't be too late</i>

507
00:41:50,449 --> 00:41:55,589
<i>Come over and hold the crying me</i>

508
00:41:55,715 --> 00:41:57,122
<i>You're the only one</i>

509
00:41:57,386 --> 00:42:02,680
<i>You're the only one in this world</i>

510
00:42:02,823 --> 00:42:05,923
<i>Who can make me laugh</i>

511
00:42:06,116 --> 00:42:09,595
<i>Now I finally realized it</i>

512
00:42:23,035 --> 00:42:28,014
<i>I want to say thank you</i>

513
00:42:29,735 --> 00:42:33,762
<i>I want to say sorry</i>

514
00:42:33,914 --> 00:42:37,192
<i>But why don't I have the courage?</i>

515
00:42:37,344 --> 00:42:42,244
<i>Why do I say hurtful words?</i>

516
00:42:42,433 --> 00:42:45,688
<i>I only realized it now</i>

517
00:42:45,843 --> 00:42:50,143
